{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0176Uu8ZpRZ8pjRJqAMFg8CJ","type":"tool_result","content":"    85→### 15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing — dev-story (2026-03-25T06:55Z)\n    86→\n    87→**Problems encountered:**\n    88→- `src/lib/scanner.ts` listed in story but has no Semgrep integration — actual Semgrep logic lives in `src/modules/observability/analyzer.ts`.\n    89→\n    90→**Workarounds applied:**\n    91→- Semgrep test fixtures use annotation format but can only validate with semgrep installed. Vitest tests validate file existence/content only.\n    92→\n    93→**Code quality concerns:**\n    94→- `no-bare-except-ellipsis` rule uses Semgrep `...` metavariable — matches ALL except bodies, not just literal Ellipsis. Correct per AC1 but name misleading.\n    95→- Hook grep pattern `except Exception.*pass` is approximate — matches comments/strings too.\n    96→\n    97→**Observations:**\n    98→- All 3799 tests pass. Zero regressions.\n    99→\n   100→### 15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing — code-review (2026-03-25T07:02Z)\n   101→\n   102→**Bugs found and fixed:**\n   103→- HIGH: Hook grep pattern `except Exception.*pass` never matches multiline Python syntax (AC2 was non-functional). Fixed with awk-based multiline detection.\n   104→- HIGH: Semgrep `no-bare-except-ellipsis` rule was false positive generator — `...` is Semgrep wildcard, not Python Ellipsis. Fixed with `pattern-regex`.\n   105→- MEDIUM: Hook only detected `pass` but not Python `...` pattern. Fixed.\n   106→- MEDIUM: AGENTS.md stale after `additionalRulesDirs` addition. Fixed.\n   107→\n   108→**Code quality issues NOT fixed:**\n   109→- Story lists `src/lib/scanner.ts` but change correctly went to `analyzer.ts` — story spec inaccuracy.\n   110→\n   111→**Coverage:** 97.11% overall, all 156 files above 80% floor.\n   112→\n   113→### Session 7 — harness-run (2026-03-25T11:15Z)\n   114→\n   115→Starting session. Scanning for actionable stories.\n   116→\n   117→### Session 8 — harness-run (2026-03-25T11:18Z)\n   118→\n   119→Starting session. Scanning for actionable stories.\n   120→\n   121→**Result:** NO_WORK — no actionable stories remain. Only 14-4-observability-backend-choice is non-done but flagged as retry-exhausted. Sprint is effectively complete at 65/66 stories (98.5%). Session was a no-op.\n   122→\n   123→### Session 9 — harness-run (2026-03-25T11:22Z)\n   124→\n   125→Starting session. Scanning for actionable stories.\n   126→\n   127→**Result:** NO_WORK — same state as sessions 7-8. 14-4-observability-backend-choice remains the only non-done story, flagged for skipping. 65/66 stories done (98.5%). Sprint effectively complete.\n   128→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"12f87d66-1054-4d11-b8f4-d0146d29b596","uuid":"8c2c914e-ba9e-4eb4-a529-8bf1a31a4aaa","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:25:35.423Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"### 15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing — dev-story (2026-03-25T06:55Z)\n\n**Problems encountered:**\n- `src/lib/scanner.ts` listed in story but has no Semgrep integration — actual Semgrep logic lives in `src/modules/observability/analyzer.ts`.\n\n**Workarounds applied:**\n- Semgrep test fixtures use annotation format but can only validate with semgrep installed. Vitest tests validate file existence/content only.\n\n**Code quality concerns:**\n- `no-bare-except-ellipsis` rule uses Semgrep `...` metavariable — matches ALL except bodies, not just literal Ellipsis. Correct per AC1 but name misleading.\n- Hook grep pattern `except Exception.*pass` is approximate — matches comments/strings too.\n\n**Observations:**\n- All 3799 tests pass. Zero regressions.\n\n### 15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing — code-review (2026-03-25T07:02Z)\n\n**Bugs found and fixed:**\n- HIGH: Hook grep pattern `except Exception.*pass` never matches multiline Python syntax (AC2 was non-functional). Fixed with awk-based multiline detection.\n- HIGH: Semgrep `no-bare-except-ellipsis` rule was false positive generator — `...` is Semgrep wildcard, not Python Ellipsis. Fixed with `pattern-regex`.\n- MEDIUM: Hook only detected `pass` but not Python `...` pattern. Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: AGENTS.md stale after `additionalRulesDirs` addition. Fixed.\n\n**Code quality issues NOT fixed:**\n- Story lists `src/lib/scanner.ts` but change correctly went to `analyzer.ts` — story spec inaccuracy.\n\n**Coverage:** 97.11% overall, all 156 files above 80% floor.\n\n### Session 7 — harness-run (2026-03-25T11:15Z)\n\nStarting session. Scanning for actionable stories.\n\n### Session 8 — harness-run (2026-03-25T11:18Z)\n\nStarting session. Scanning for actionable stories.\n\n**Result:** NO_WORK — no actionable stories remain. Only 14-4-observability-backend-choice is non-done but flagged as retry-exhausted. Sprint is effectively complete at 65/66 stories (98.5%). Session was a no-op.\n\n### Session 9 — harness-run (2026-03-25T11:22Z)\n\nStarting session. Scanning for actionable stories.\n\n**Result:** NO_WORK — same state as sessions 7-8. 14-4-observability-backend-choice remains the only non-done story, flagged for skipping. 65/66 stories done (98.5%). Sprint effectively complete.\n","numLines":44,"startLine":85,"totalLines":128}}}
